=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>OS 扩容适配</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>系统版本确认</li>\n<li>硬盘利用状况确认</li>\n<li>工具安装</li>\n<li>扩容</li>\n<li>重启</li>\n<li>文件系统适配</li>\n<li>确认</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"1-系统版本确认\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4\" aria-label=\"1 系统版本确认 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#1-%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4\" aria-label=\"1 系统版本确认 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 系统版本确认</h3>\n<deckgo-highlight-code shell  terminal=\"carbon\" line-numbers=\"true\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">[ec2-user ~]# cat /etc/issue\nCentOS release 6.5 (Final)\nKernel \\r on an \\m</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h3 id=\"2-硬盘利用状况确认\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E7%8A%B6%E5%86%B5%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4\" aria-label=\"2 硬盘利用状况确认 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#2-%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E7%8A%B6%E5%86%B5%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4\" aria-label=\"2 硬盘利用状况确认 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 硬盘利用状况确认</h3>\n<deckgo-highlight-code shell  terminal=\"carbon\" line-numbers=\"true\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">[ec2-user ~]# df -hT\nFilesystem     Type   Size  Used Avail Use% Mounted on\n/dev/xvda1     ext4    8G   4G  4G  50% /\n\n[ec2-user ~]# lsblk\nNAME    MAJ:MIN RM SIZE RO TYPE MOUNTPOINT\nxvda    202:0    0  30G  0 disk \n└─xvda1 202:1    0  8G  0 part /</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<ul>\n<li>注意Type列，一般的类型有两种Ext4或者xfs，后面会用到</li>\n<li>通过lsblk查看卷号，xvda1</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3-工具安装\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\" aria-label=\"3 工具安装 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#3-%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\" aria-label=\"3 工具安装 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 工具安装</h3>\n<p>推荐使用growpart</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code shell  terminal=\"carbon\" line-numbers=\"true\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">[ec2-user ~]# yum install -y epel-release\n[ec2-user ~]# yum install -y --enablerepo=epel cloud-utils-growpart\n[ec2-user ~]# yum install -y --enablerepo=epel dracut-modules-growroot</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>如有如下错误</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code shell  terminal=\"carbon\" line-numbers=\"true\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">[ec2-user ~]# yum install -y epel-release\nLoaded plugins: fastestmirror, presto\nDetermining fastest mirrors\nYumRepo Error: All mirror URLs are not using ftp, http[s] or file.\n Eg. Invalid release/repo/arch combination/\nremoving mirrorlist with no valid mirrors: /var/cache/yum/x86_64/6/base/mirrorlist.txt\nError: Cannot find a valid baseurl for repo: base</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>更改URL后，再次安装</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code shell  terminal=\"carbon\" line-numbers=\"true\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">[ec2-user ~]# sed -i -e &quot;s/^mirrorlist=http:\\/\\/mirrorlist.centos.org/#mirrorlist=http:\\/\\/mirrorlist.centos.org/g&quot; /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo\n[ec2-user ~]# sed -i -e &quot;s/^#baseurl=http:\\/\\/mirror.centos.org/baseurl=http:\\/\\/vault.centos.org/g&quot; /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo\n[ec2-user ~]# yum install -y epel-release\n[ec2-user ~]# yum install -y --enablerepo=epel cloud-utils-growpart\n[ec2-user ~]# yum install -y --enablerepo=epel dracut-modules-growroot</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h3 id=\"4-扩容\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-%E6%89%A9%E5%AE%B9\" aria-label=\"4 扩容 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#4-%E6%89%A9%E5%AE%B9\" aria-label=\"4 扩容 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. 扩容</h3>\n<deckgo-highlight-code shell  terminal=\"carbon\" line-numbers=\"true\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">[ec2-user ~]# export LANG=&quot;en_US.UTF-8&quot;\n[ec2-user ~]# growpart /dev/xvda 1</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<ul>\n<li>注意数字1，通过步骤2的命令查看。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"5-重启os\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-%E9%87%8D%E5%90%AFos\" aria-label=\"5 重启os permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#5-%E9%87%8D%E5%90%AFos\" aria-label=\"5 重启os permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. 重启OS</h3>\n<deckgo-highlight-code shell  terminal=\"carbon\" line-numbers=\"true\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">[ec2-user ~]# reboot</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h3 id=\"6-文件系统适配\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#6-%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E9%80%82%E9%85%8D\" aria-label=\"6 文件系统适配 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#6-%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E9%80%82%E9%85%8D\" aria-label=\"6 文件系统适配 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6. 文件系统适配</h3>\n<p>XFS类型时（通过步骤2查看）</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code shell  terminal=\"carbon\" line-numbers=\"true\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">[ec2-user ~]$ xfs_growfs /dev/xvda1</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<ul>\n<li>xfs_growfs安装</li>\n</ul>\n<deckgo-highlight-code shell  terminal=\"carbon\" line-numbers=\"true\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">[ec2-user ~]$ yum install -y --enablerepo=epel xfsprogs</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>ext4类型时（通过步骤2查看）</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code shell  terminal=\"carbon\" line-numbers=\"true\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">[ec2-user ~]$ sudo resize2fs /dev/xvda1</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h3 id=\"7-确认\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#7-%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4\" aria-label=\"7 确认 permalink\" class=\"anchor before